# FinLens Environment Variables
#
# NOTE: This app does not currently require a .env file to run.
# All API keys (GitHub, Anthropic, OpenAI, Gemini) are entered by the user
# directly in the app's Settings modal and stored in the browser's localStorage.
# They are never sent to any server other than the respective AI provider's API.
#
# The only variable read at build time is VITE_BASE_PATH (optional, see below).

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Build configuration (optional)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Base URL path for the app. Set this if you are deploying to a subdirectory.
# Defaults to '/finlens-app/' which matches the GitHub Pages URL structure.
# For local dev or a root-level deployment, set to '/'.
# VITE_BASE_PATH=/finlens-app/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# API keys — NOT used here. Entered by the user in Settings > API Keys.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# GitHub Personal Access Token
#   Used for: GitHub Sync (backing up data to a private gist or repo)
#   Permissions needed: gist (read/write) or repo (read/write)
#   Enter in: Settings modal → GitHub Sync tab
# GITHUB_TOKEN=

# Anthropic API Key
#   Used for: AI transaction categorization via Claude
#   Enter in: Settings modal → AI Categorization tab
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# OpenAI API Key
#   Used for: AI transaction categorization via GPT models
#   Enter in: Settings modal → AI Categorization tab
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Google Gemini API Key
#   Used for: AI transaction categorization via Gemini models
#   Enter in: Settings modal → AI Categorization tab
# GEMINI_API_KEY=
